				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$20\mathrm{mm}\times 20\mathrm{mm},$$\end{document} respectively and well-suited for the S-band waveguide.Figure 1
Layout of the proposed metamaterial unit cell.

